item.title: CVE-2019-0314|2024-08-04T17:44:16.468Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20work%20manager
item.description: SAP Work Manager, versions: 6.3, 6.4, 6.5 and SAP Inventory Manager, version 4.3, allows an attacker to prevent legitimate users from accessing a service, either by crashing or flooding the service.
